Subject: [PATCH 28/30] ntfs: use sb_bdev_nr_blocks
Date:   Mon, 18 Oct 2021 12:11:28 +0200
Message-Id: <20211018101130.1838532-29-hch@lst.de>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
